                  SizedBox(height: context.screenHeight * 0.01),
                  Text('Global Connect is committed to ensuring that our Service is compliant with all applicable data protection laws and regulations, including the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR).', style: pjsStyleBlack14400),
                  SizedBox(height: context.screenHeight * 0.02),
                  Text('3.1. Your Privacy and Transparency', style: pjsStyleBlack14600),
                  SizedBox(height: context.screenHeight * 0.01),
                  Text('3.1.1. Transparency and accountability are very important to us at Global Connect. We provide detailed information about how we process your personal data in our Privacy Policy (or Privacy Statement). This policy outlines exactly what personal data we collect, why we collect it, how we use it, who we share it with, and your rights regarding your data. It also includes information about the service providers and subcontractors we use to process your data, and where our data centers are located.', style: pjsStyleBlack14400),
                  SizedBox(height: context.screenHeight * 0.01),
                  Text('Our full Privacy Policy is always available on our website at www.global-connect.ai', style: pjsStyleBlack14400),
                  SizedBox(height: context.screenHeight * 0.01),
